{"content": "I need to multiply 347\u2089 \u00d7 817\u2089.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n347\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 4\u00d79\u00b9 + 7\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 7\u00d71 = 243 + 36 + 7 = 286\u2081\u2080\n\n817\u2089 = 8\u00d79\u00b2 + 1\u00d79\u00b9 + 7\u00d79\u2070 = 8\u00d781 + 1\u00d79 + 7\u00d71 = 648 + 9 + 7 = 664\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n286 \u00d7 664 = 189,904\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n189904 \u00f7 9 = 21100 r 4\n21100 \u00f7 9 = 2344 r 4\n2344 \u00f7 9 = 260 r 4\n260 \u00f7 9 = 28 r 8\n28 \u00f7 9 = 3 r 1\n3 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 3\n\nReading from bottom to top: 318444\u2089\n\n**Step 4: Verification**\n\n318444\u2089 = 3\u00d759049 + 1\u00d76561 + 8\u00d7729 + 4\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 4\u00d71\n= 177147 + 6561 + 5832 + 324 + 36 + 4\n= 189904\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n318444", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1150, "completion_tokens": 416}